OL,3,CCan Reeves increase investment and
OL,4,Cavoid austerity?
OL,6,FThere are two levers or seesaws that
OL,7,Fwill determine the success or failure
OL,8,Fof Rachel Reeves's momentous budget on
OL,9,FOctober 30 - a budget that will
OL,10,Fdetermine whether this government
OL,11,Fmoves to calmer waters from the
OL,12,Fcurrent buffeting.
OL,14,FThey are a debt/interest seesaw and a
OL,15,Ftax/private-sector-investment lever.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
