OL,3,CCan Reeves increase investment and
OL,4,Cavoid austerity?
OL,6,FAnd what these seesaws make incredibly
OL,7,Fdifficult for Reeves is to achieve she
OL,8,Fand Starmer's twin stated ambitions
OL,9,Fwhich are to increase productive
OL,10,Finvestment while avoiding public-
OL,11,Fservice austerity.
OL,13,FHere is why.
OL,15,FThe first lever balances increased
OL,16,Fpublic-sector investment financed by
OL,17,Fadditional borrowing against the
OL,18,Fincrease in interest payments that
OL,19,Fwill be loaded on taxpayers from this
OL,20,Fincrement to public sector debt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
