OL,3,CCan Reeves increase investment and
OL,4,Cavoid austerity?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FRachel Reeves's decision to change one
OL,12,Fof her fiscal rules from a target to
OL,13,Freduce gross debt as a share of GDP in
OL,14,Ffive years time to one of growing net
OL,15,Fworth (debt minus the value of created
OL,16,Fassets) is still murky in the detail.
OL,17,FBut the principle is clear: it will
OL,18,Fallow her to borrow tens of billions
OL,19,Fof pounds more for productive
OL,20,Finvestment in the lifetime of this
OL,21,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
