OL,3,CCan Reeves increase investment and
OL,4,Cavoid austerity?
OL,6,FYou will immediately grasp, therefore,
OL,7,Fthat if she borrows colossal sums for
OL,8,Finvestment, the interest that the
OL,9,Fgovernment would shell out on the
OL,10,Fincreased debt would limit the amount
OL,11,Fof cash available to pay for pensions,
OL,12,Fsocial security and nurses wages,
OL,13,Finter alia.
OL,15,FOr at least that would be the limiting
OL,16,Fcondition in the coming few years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
