OL,3,CCan Reeves increase investment and
OL,4,Cavoid austerity?
OL,6,FThereafter the investments she has
OL,7,Ffinanced - in green energy, and
OL,8,Ftransport, and housing - should
OL,9,Fincrease the nation's productivity and
OL,10,Fgrowth, which in turn would boost tax
OL,11,Frevenues.
OL,13,FBut in the words of a recent Office
OL,14,Ffor Budget Responsibility report, "a
OL,15,Fsustained 1 per cent of GDP increase
OL,16,Fin public investment could plausibly
OL,17,Fincrease the level of potential output
OL,18,Fby just under \ a percent after five
OL,19,Fyears and around 2\ per cent in the
OL,20,Flong run (50 years)".
