OL,3,CCan Reeves increase investment and
OL,4,Cavoid austerity?
OL,6,FWhich takes us to the second lever,
OL,7,Fbetween the benefits of increasing
OL,8,Ftaxes and the disbenefits of
OL,9,Fconsequentially discouraging private-
OL,10,Fsector investment.
OL,12,FThere are two substantial tax changes
OL,13,FReeves is considering, and they both
OL,14,Fhave significant implications for
OL,15,Fprivate-sector businesses.
OL,17,FOne is to make employers' pension
OL,18,Fcontributions liable to national
OL,19,Finsurance. And the other is to raise
OL,20,Fthe rates of capital gains tax.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
