OL,3,CCan Reeves increase investment and
OL,4,Cavoid austerity?
OL,6,FWhen it comes to CGT increases, one
OL,7,Flimiting factor is simply that owners
OL,8,Fwould hang onto their assets longer to
OL,9,Favoid crystallizing a liability or
OL,10,Fwould move abroad to avoid it
OL,11,Faltogether if the tax rate were
OL,12,Fincreased very significantly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
