OL,3,CCan Reeves increase investment and
OL,4,Cavoid austerity?
OL,6,FBut for both taxes the more important
OL,7,Flimiting factor is the way they would
OL,8,Fincrease business costs, dampen animal
OL,9,Fspirits and economic activity, and
OL,10,Ftherefore reduce private-sector
OL,11,Finvestment, at a time when our entire
OL,12,Ffuture prosperity as a nation hinges
OL,13,Fon whether the government can end
OL,14,Fdecades of relative under-investment
OL,15,Fin the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
