OL,3,CCan Reeves increase investment and
OL,4,Cavoid austerity?
OL,6,FSo here is the nutshell of Reeves's
OL,7,Fquandary: if she borrows too much to
OL,8,Ffinance desperately needed investment
OL,9,Fin crumbling infrastructure, the
OL,10,Finevitable interest bill adds to the
OL,11,Fpressure on her to put up taxes, which
OL,12,Fthen discourages equally vital private-
OL,13,Fsector investment.
OL,15,FIt is a nightmare for her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
